<item>
            <title>[LU-3225] Timeout failure on test suite sanity-quota, subtest test_19</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3225</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for Nathaniel Clark &amp;lt;nathaniel.l.clark@intel.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite runs:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;http://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/3266c9e6-a2df-11e2-a7df-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/3266c9e6-a2df-11e2-a7df-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
